	(5578,94,'wpcf-biography','I am a Chilean Independent graphic artist and designer, confused still if I am doing art, design or what. I have collaborated in different art collectives: Kiltraza, Alambique Veloz (experimental punk band), Ergocomics (comic), among others. In 2004, I joined to TROYANO, media art collective oriented to develop projects on the relation between art, science and technology. \r\n\r\nAs a designer and artist I have collaborated in differents books and exhibitions in Chile and abroad, participating in many visuals presentations, colaborating with  artistas and musicians, like Mankacen (Alejandro Albornoz), Pueblo Nuevo and the danish musician Lars Gaaugard. \r\n\r\nMy current interests are focused on understanding the recent technological processes, in a framework that includes concepts of biological evolution, social and economic issues. \r\n\r\nWith my girlfriend wife María José Ríos (VyV), have creating the visual-sonic project “01″, participating in many concerts in Santiago de Chile.\r\n\r\nThe most important project now is raise Alicia, my daughter.'),
