	(6863,565,'wpcf-short-description','Digital interactive story addressing environmental change that combines 2D and 3D platforms.'),
	(6864,565,'wpcf-long-description','For my thesis project, I am making an interactive digital children’s book that tells a story about a changing utopia that adapts to its environment. The interaction will allow the user to control the viewpoint of the camera in each page and will also allow them to explore the environment freely by walking through it. Each page will also be animated individually, where the setting comes alive. This way, they reader will get engaged in the story. My project combines a gaming environment with a digital book narrative, which gives an interesting approach to storytelling.'),
