	(6993,61,'wpcf-biography','My name is Jason — sometimes I use the stage name dada powell. I formed Dada Powell Industries to house my creative work, the bulk of which is web development, hip-hop music and performances. My goal is to apply fine art principles to rap and expand the aesthetic possibilities of rap performance using new media strategies. I also enjoy building websites, creating self-portraits, drawing people on the train, and doodling.'),
