	(7714,525,'wpcf-long-description','Dumb Songs is a two-player musical toy which illustrates how a playful mind makes for better collaboration and creativity, so that I can show the power of creation play, a type of play that results in a complete creative artifact at its conclusion.\r\n\r\nIt uses physical controllers to send MIDI notes and control signals to Ableton Live to create a musical environment for two people to play in. The touchability of the controls combined with the light and whimsical treatment of its display engenders a childlike abandon amongst its players that better facilitates a fun and creative experience.'),
