	(13557,572,'wpcf-long-description','This project is about a group of twelve machines. They get life from mimicking human traits and actuating different kinds of motion mechanisms when powered by electricity. The machines perform a scenario of a lap dance being surrounded by another eleven machine viewers. Each viewer has its unique reaction to the dance. The dance itself features a merged entity that consists of a dancer and one that receives the dance. Intrinsically, the project is a performance of machines having fun by themselves, while a human maid providing services such as keeping the floor clean, maintaining the electronics, and cutting the power off every now and then in case the machines die a horrible death from overdosing themselves.'),
