	(14454,542,'wpcf-short-description','Wearable Technology'),
	(14455,542,'wpcf-long-description','HIDE raises awareness of cruelty to animals in service of fashion. The focus is the fur trade and the pain animals suffer due to trapping and farming practices. Experiencing or facing qualitative nature within wearable technology to self-aware of the horrifying inconvenient truth, I expect people to gain the knowledge and awakening themselves about fur trade. It denounces the torture and slaying of animals to make fur coats and to evoke animals’ horrifying death. Hide reveals truth of the cost of supporting the fur industry; therefore consumers reconsider to buy fur products with their own initiative in the future. Hide is created with new medium and technology to efficiently deliver the new experience to the participants. Using wearable technology, audiences consciousness are rising due to its contradictory look. The goal of this project is to emotionally persuade people to rethink about what beauty is by educating consumers about inherently inhumane farming and trapping of fur-bearing animals.'),
