	(14519,64,'wpcf-long-description','Peaches is a two-player game about cooperation and conflict. Using fairy-tale tropes, it casts the players as knight and princess, bound together to achieve their goal, forced to cooperate, if only awkwardly. But as with all cooperation, potential conflict lurks beneath the surface, and their relationship becomes more complex as the game continues.\r\n \r\nThe game also plays with a few gender stereotypes, including the ever-popular damsel in distress, but that\'s really just for extra fun.'),
