	(15016,102,'wpcf-biography','Animation designer from the Netherlands. In my work I experiment with alternative ways of communicating complex ideas, using a mix of traditional and modern techniques like stop-motion and computer animation. I study propaganda and old feature films, especially how they used to communicate their message, and use that as inspiration to explain and summarize complex ideas. I use visual language, metaphors, symbolism, context-driven association and suggestion, but also rhythm, music and sound for the development of my own non-verbal lexicon.'),
