	(16878,556,'wpcf-short-description','Flocking is a mobile application that allows its users to discover and share fleeting events occurring nearby.'),
	(16879,556,'wpcf-long-description','You want to explore, be spontaneous, live freely, do new and exciting things. You don\'t want to be tied down to a schedule, but instead want the ability to change courses throughout your day, pivot, decide what you want to do when you have the time to do it. We all do. We just didn\'t know we could with our limiting schedules. \r\n\r\nFlocking is a guide for explorers, it lets users discover all the exciting events they are near, giving them a chance to experience them before they are gone for good. The community posts about events they are attending, while others vote on what is most appealing to them. This provides users of the application with a real time map of all the popular events currently occurring near them that they could attend.'),
